---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const meta = {
  title: 'Relume AI Review: AI Website Builder for Webflow (2025)',
  description: 'Relume AI generates Webflow-ready sitemaps and wireframes in seconds. Free for individuals. Great for designers starting projects. Not a full website builder. Works with Webflow, Figma. Complete review.',
  image: '/og-image.svg',
  keywords: ['Relume AI review', 'AI website builder', 'Relume Webflow', 'AI sitemap generator', 'Relume pricing'],
};
---

<Layout {...meta}>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0A0A0A]/5 to-[#FF6B35]/5 py-12 sm:py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <p class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs font-black text-[#FF6B35] mb-4 tracking-[0.3em] uppercase">
        AI Tool Review · 2025 Updated
      </p>

      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black mb-6 leading-tight">
        Relume AI Review
      </h1>

      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-700 mb-8">
        Relume AI generates website sitemaps and wireframes in seconds. It's designed for Webflow and Figma, not as a standalone website builder. The free tier is generous for individuals. Pro plans add collaboration. This is a starting tool, not a complete solution. You'll still build the actual site in Webflow or Figma.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-50 border-2 border-gray-300 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
          Quick answer: Relume AI is excellent for designers who use Webflow or Figma. It generates sitemaps and wireframes fast. Free for individuals makes it a no-brainer to try. It won't build your finished site - you still design in Webflow/Figma. Think of it as AI-powered brainstorming and planning tool, not a website builder.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What It Is -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      What Relume AI Is (and Isn't)
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">What Relume AI Does</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Generates sitemaps:</strong> Enter your business, get complete site structure</li>
          <li>• <strong>Creates wireframes:</strong> Visual layouts for every page</li>
          <li>• <strong>Exports to Webflow:</strong> Copy-paste directly into Webflow</li>
          <li>• <strong>Exports to Figma:</strong> Continue designing in Figma</li>
          <li>• <strong>Uses components:</strong> Pre-built sections you can customize</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-red-50 border-2 border-red-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">What Relume AI Doesn't Do</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Not a website builder:</strong> Can't host your site</li>
          <li>• <strong>No final design:</strong> Wireframes, not finished designs</li>
          <li>• <strong>No AI content generation:</strong> Creates structure, not copy</li>
          <li>• <strong>No hosting:</strong> Still need Webflow or hosting</li>
          <li>• <strong>No CMS:</strong> Still need to build that yourself</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      Relume AI Pricing
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">Starter (Free) - Best for Individuals</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Price:</strong> Free forever</li>
          <li>• <strong>Unlimited projects:</strong> No limit on sitemaps/wireframes</li>
          <li>• <strong>Full library access:</strong> All components available</li>
          <li>• <strong>Webflow export:</strong> Copy to Webflow</li>
          <li>• <strong>Figma export:</strong> Continue in Figma</li>
          <li>• <strong>Community support:</strong> Help from community</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Value:</strong> Incredible value for freelancers and individual designers. No reason not to use it if you use Webflow or Figma.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">Pro ($32/month or $288/year)</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Everything in Starter, plus:</strong></li>
          <li>• <strong>Team collaboration:</strong> Multiple users on projects</li>
          <li>• <strong>Shared library:</strong> Team-wide component access</li>
          <li>• <strong>Priority support:</strong> Faster help when needed</li>
          <li>• <strong>Early access:</strong> New features first</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Value:</strong> For agencies and teams. If you're solo, free tier has everything you need.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Key Features -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      Key Features
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">1. AI Sitemap Generation</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Enter your business info, get complete site structure:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Industry-specific:</strong> Knows what restaurants need vs agencies</li>
          <li>• <strong>Hierarchy:</strong> Logical page organization</li>
          <li>• <strong>Editable:</strong> Add/remove pages as needed</li>
          <li>• <strong>Best practices:</strong> Follows modern site structure</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Why it matters:</strong> Sitemeps take hours to plan. AI generates in seconds.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">2. Wireframe Components</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Pre-built sections you customize:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Heros, features, testimonials:</strong> All standard sections</li>
          <li>• <strong>Consistent design:</strong> Matches your brand style</li>
          <li>• <strong>Responsive:</strong> Mobile, tablet, desktop layouts</li>
          <li>• <strong>Webflow-ready:</strong> Designed for Webflow structure</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Why it matters:</strong> Don't start from blank. Iterate on proven patterns.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">3. Webflow Integration</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Built specifically for Webflow:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Copy-paste:</strong> Direct export to Webflow</li>
          <li>• <strong>Clean code:</strong> Semantic structure Webflow expects</li>
          <li>• <strong>Classes named:</strong> Ready to style in Webflow</li>
          <li>• <strong>Saves hours:</strong> Skip initial structure building</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Why it matters:</strong> Webflow is powerful but time-consuming. Relume speeds up starting phase.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">4. Figma Integration</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Export to Figma for design work:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Figma frames:</strong> Proper layer structure</li>
          <li>• <strong>Editable:</strong> Full design control in Figma</li>
          <li>• <strong>Auto-layout:</strong> Uses Figma auto-layout</li>
          <li>• <strong>Components:</strong> Figma components maintained</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Why it matters:</strong> Design in Figma, then build in Webflow. Smooth workflow.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Use Cases -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      Who Relume AI is For
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">✅ Perfect For</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Webflow designers:</strong> Speed up project starts dramatically</li>
          <li>• <strong>Figma designers:</strong> Quick wireframes before detailed design</li>
          <li>• <strong>Freelancers:</strong> Free tier is perfect for solo work</li>
          <li>• <strong>Agencies:</strong> Faster onboarding for new projects</li>
          <li>• <strong>People planning sites:</strong> Visualize structure before building</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-red-50 border-2 border-red-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">❌ Not For</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Non-designers:</strong> Still need Webflow/Figma skills</li>
          <li>• <strong>Quick simple sites:</strong> Overkill for basic landing page</li>
          <li>• <strong>People who don't use Webflow/Figma:</strong> Integrations required</li>
          <li>• <strong>Finished websites:</strong> Need to design and build yourself</li>
          <li>• <strong>Content creation:</strong> Doesn't write copy or content</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pros and Cons -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      Pros and Cons
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">Pros</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Free for individuals:</strong> Generous free tier</li>
          <li>• <strong>Fast:</strong> Sitemaps and wireframes in seconds</li>
          <li>• <strong>Webflow integration:</strong> Built specifically for Webflow</li>
          <li>• <strong>Figma integration:</strong> Also works with Figma</li>
          <li>• <strong>Quality components:</strong> Professional, modern designs</li>
          <li>• <strong>Time saver:</strong> Cuts hours from project starts</li>
          <li>• <strong>No lock-in:</strong> Export and keep working in your tools</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-red-50 border-2 border-red-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">Cons</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Not a website builder:</strong> Can't host your finished site</li>
          <li>• <strong>Webflow/Figma required:</strong> Useless without these tools</li>
          <li>• <strong>Wireframes only:</strong> Not finished designs</li>
          <li>• <strong>No content generation:</strong> Structure, not copy</li>
          <li>• <strong>Learning curve still exists:</strong> Still need to learn Webflow/Figma</li>
          <li>• <strong>Limited customization:</strong> Working within component system</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Alternatives -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      Alternatives to Consider
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-300 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">Durable</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4"><strong>For:</strong> Service businesses who need complete websites fast</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4"><strong>Price:</strong> $15/month</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Generates full websites with AI-written content. Not wireframes - actual finished sites. Better if you want a working site, not planning tools.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-300 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">v0.dev</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4"><strong>For:</strong> Developers who want AI-generated React code</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4"><strong>Price:</strong> Free</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Generates React components from prompts. For developers building with code, not visual designers. Different tool for different audience.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-300 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">Framer</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4"><strong>For:</strong> Designers who want visual website builder</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4"><strong>Price:</strong> $16/month</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Full website builder with design control. No wireframing stage - just design and publish. Faster if you want to skip planning and build directly.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-300 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">Webflow (Direct)</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4"><strong>For:</strong> Designers comfortable starting from blank</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4"><strong>Price:</strong> $14/month</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Use Webflow directly if you don't need AI help with sitemaps. Relume speeds up planning, but isn't required.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bottom Line -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-50 border-2 border-gray-300 rounded-xl p-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-black mb-6">Bottom Line</h2>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">Relume AI is a specialized tool for Webflow and Figma designers. It generates sitemaps and wireframes, not finished websites.</p>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6"><strong>Use Relume AI if:</strong></p>
      <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
        <li>• You use Webflow or Figma regularly</li>
        <li>• You want to speed up project planning phase</li>
        <li>• You like working from proven patterns</li>
        <li>• You're solo freelancer (free tier is perfect)</li>
        <li>• You want AI-assisted brainstorming for site structure</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6"><strong>Skip Relume AI if:</strong></p>
      <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
        <li>• You don't use Webflow or Figma</li>
        <li>• You want a complete website builder</li>
        <li>• You need AI-generated content/copy</li>
        <li>• You prefer starting from blank canvas</li>
        <li>• You're building simple one-page site</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700"><strong>Bottom line:</strong> If you're a Webflow or Figma designer, try the free tier. No reason not to. If it saves you time on one project, it's worth it. If you're not a designer, this tool isn't for you - look at Durable, Framer, or Webflow directly.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Related -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black mb-6 text-gray-900">
      Related Reviews
    </h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <a href="/webflow-review" class="block bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-6 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Webflow Review</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">No-code powerhouse review</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/durable-review" class="block bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-6 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Durable Review</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">AI website builder review</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
